**Lab 6: Implementing Helm Package Management in EKS**
**Objective**: Explore Helm as a package manager for Kubernetes applications.
**Tasks**:
1. Install Helm in your EKS cluster.
2. Deploy a chart.
3. Update and roll back using Helm.

Step#1
install helm
Website :
https://helm.sh/docs/intro/install/

helm version

Step#2


cd my-repo

kubectl config current-context

Step#3

helm install my-repo .

Kubectl get pods

ls

Step#4
vi values.yaml


Change cluster-ip to LoadBalancer

helm upgrade my-repo .

kubectl get svc

